          /Info (none)
         /Type /OutputIntent
        /S /GTS_PDFX
       /OutputConditionIdentifier (OFCOM_PO_P1_F60_95)
      /RegistryName (http://www.color.org/)
      >> ]
          }'                                            >> ${TMPID}.preamble
   }

 # ------------------------------------------------------------------------- # 
 # DO IT AT THE END 
